b-0" value=3D"1"><strong><strong class=3D"font-bold">LED:</strong></strong>=
<span> Lumens =3D Watts x 80</span></li>
<li class=3D"text-body font-regular text-gray-800 leading-[24px] my-[5px] [=
&amp;&gt;ol]:!pt-0 [&amp;&gt;ol]:!pb-0 [&amp;&gt;ul]:!pt-0 [&amp;&gt;ul]:!p=
b-0" value=3D"2"><strong><strong class=3D"font-bold">CFL:</strong></strong>=
